{"tid":1479680,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"一眼睇哂精選Post - Trello 版","createTime":"2019-08-17T04:03:37.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-16T15:20:09.000Z","uid":41355,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"d641dc9a32e00343f936400f654ed6c234cea55c","tid":1479680,"uid":41355,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-17T04:03:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/UaqE3ay.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FUaqE3ay.png&h=3bdd44bc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n我地用trello整左個連登精華post集合<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">將即日重要、高質既討論post集合埋一齊、帶番上水</span><br />\n將相關既post分類+放埋一齊，簡潔呈現唔同種類既POST，等大家更容易搵到相關既post<br />\n除左可以將沉左底但重要既post拎番出黎之外，都可以<span style=\"color: red;\">避免帶風向</span>既情況<br />\n每幾個鐘update一次<br />\n有興趣既巴絲可以bookmark左佢<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://trello.com/b/IRrY8V1N/%E5%8F%8D%E9%80%81%E4%B8%ADlihkg-portal\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftrello.com%2Fb%2FIRrY8V1N%2F%25E5%258F%258D%25E9%2580%2581%25E4%25B8%25ADlihkg-portal&d=u3dPEc69Okhs1BcqxCk75Qy7VxIBYRqzliHj24KwcnI%3D&h=226a891d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://trello.com/b/IRrY8V1N/%E5%8F%8D%E9%80%81%E4%B8%ADlihkg-portal</a>"},{"pid":"40f25eeb9c5fe6824ef623762e6e2c5dfa3f1b37","tid":1479680,"uid":41355,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-17T04:07:58.000Z","msg":"<strong>／包括啲咩post</strong><br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">以討論、資訊為主</span></strong><br />\n類別包括：行動方向、文宣方向、戰術討論、支援行動、賽後檢討等<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong>／唔包括啲咩post</strong><br />\n1. 無即時既行動資訊，因為已有612 reminder等tg channel<br />\n2. 無文宣集合<br />\n3. 唔係黑警資料庫<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong>／可以點樣幫手？</strong><br />\n需要人幫手報料同update Trello<br />\n留意下有咩重要既討論post我地無放到上去<br />\n同埋需要幫手cross check，避免被帶風向既情況<br />\n<br />\n想報料既手足可以係度留言<br />\n想幫手update既手足可以留低tg，我地add你入channel<br />\n我地想向ig/fb進發，將討論帶出連登以外既地方<br />\n但依家未夠人手"},{"pid":"d17d1bf4749e38afd510d8c4c8616414da7cc07b","tid":1479680,"uid":118360,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-17T04:38:25.000Z","msg":"想問下有無裝備 list?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f973ee3bdcb5b9fb3aa6568c35cd2d5ceccb6f27","tid":1479680,"uid":41355,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-17T04:53:01.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"6f065fd7dc2201d6dc14eef23e6a58a636fe23cf","tid":1479680,"uid":41355,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d17d1bf4749e38afd510d8c4c8616414da7cc07b","tid":1479680,"uid":118360,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-17T04:38:25.000Z","msg":"想問下有無裝備 list?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-17T04:53:40.000Z","msg":"有呀<br />\n拉去右面&quot;裝備/醫療/後勤&quot;個度"},{"pid":"2afefd60a9b590540a8e0b8a222d924eb3c39ebc","tid":1479680,"uid":118360,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6f065fd7dc2201d6dc14eef23e6a58a636fe23cf","tid":1479680,"uid":41355,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d17d1bf4749e38afd510d8c4c8616414da7cc07b","tid":1479680,"uid":118360,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-17T04:38:25.000Z","msg":"想問下有無裝備 list?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-17T04:53:40.000Z","msg":"有呀<br />\n拉去右面&quot;裝備/醫療/後勤&quot;個度"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-17T05:13:36.000Z","msg":"thx + 推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"07ed9